OL,3,COn-trial son admits he 'should have
OL,4,Cdone more' to help malnourished mother
OL,6,FA man has admitted he "should have
OL,7,Fdone more" to care for his elderly
OL,8,Fmother and accepted he didn't call for
OL,9,Fhelp while she was "withering away"
OL,10,Fbefore her death.
OL,12,FDavid Holyoak, 53, and 61-year-old
OL,13,FRobert Christopher Morgan ` known as
OL,14,FChris ` are on trial at Carlisle Crown
OL,15,FCourt.
OL,17,FHolyoak and Morgan deny a manslaughter
OL,18,Fcharge which alleges that they
OL,19,Funlawfully killed their respective
OL,20,Fmother and wife, 71-year-old Dorothy
OL,21,FMorgan, by gross negligence.
