OL,3,COn-trial son admits he 'should have
OL,4,Cdone more' to help malnourished mother
OL,6,FMrs Morgan, who lived with the men at
OL,7,FCalder Avenue, Whitehaven, died at the
OL,8,FWest Cumberland Hospital in February
OL,9,F2021, more than a week after she was
OL,10,Fadmitted.
OL,12,FMedical staff found 5ft 1in Mrs Morgan
OL,13,Fwas clinically dehydrated, severely
OL,14,Fmalnourished and weighed only four-and-
OL,15,Fa-half stones.
OL,17,FA pathologist concluded she died from
OL,18,Fsevere emaciation and neglected
OL,19,Finfected pressure ulcers. On Friday
OL,20,FHolyoak ` her son by another man `
OL,21,Fgave evidence.
