OL,3,COn-trial son admits he 'should have
OL,4,Cdone more' to help malnourished mother
OL,6,F"I don't remember any," said Holyoak.
OL,8,FIn the October, his friend had said by
OL,9,Ftext: "I'm going to say this sounds
OL,10,Flike you are watching a lady die."
OL,12,FA second message from the woman read:
OL,13,F"Honey, do you want her to see a
OL,14,Fdoctor or let her wither away? Please
OL,15,Fjust be honest."
OL,17,FMr Simkin asked: "Did you want her to
OL,18,Fwither away?"
OL,20,F"No," replied Holyoak."
