OL,6,FThe prosecutor suggested: "You didn't
OL,7,Fcare for her properly, or at all,
OL,8,Freally, did you?
OL,10,F"I should have done more," replied
OL,11,FHolyoak. "I didn't acknowledge that
OL,12,F(she might be dying). I didn't want it
OL,13,Fto be true. I didn't accept it as
OL,14,Fbeing true. I didn't want to accept it
OL,15,Fas being true."
OL,17,FMr Simkin suggested: "But you knew it
OL,18,Fwas true."
