OL,6,F"We tried to get her to eat," he said.
OL,8,F"We tried but we couldn't physically
OL,9,Fforce her to eat if she didn't want
OL,10,Fto."
OL,12,FWhen asked the same question in
OL,13,Frelation to water, Holyoak responded:
OL,14,F"As far as I knew she was taking
OL,15,Fwater."
OL,17,F"You must accept," suggested Mr
OL,18,FSimkin, "that you didn't check
OL,19,Fproperly. Otherwise she wouldn't have
OL,20,Fbecome dehydrated."
